FBIS3-32627 "drlat030_a_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-030 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Feb 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Groups Warn U.S. Interest Section Seized by Extremists PA1202052394 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 0455 GMT 12 Feb 94 PA1202052394 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Today, organizations of Cubans in the United States warned that the Washington government office in charge of transmitting subversive propaganda is virtually in the hands of extremists. This week, the new director of [words indistinct] Lobo, who is identified as an ally of the groups that are opposed to the Cuban revolutionary system.
